rows.label: qst700402_msg0001
rows.name:
Wow... It's like something
out of a painting...

rows.label: qst700402_msg0002
rows.name: Get back Laura. I'll clear the way.

rows.label: qst700402_msg0004
rows.name:
Look around you Shin. Is it just the
Gogols keeping a tight formation?

rows.label: qst700402_msg0005
rows.name:
We're stronger as a single unit.
If you go off on your own, you're
leaving yourself wide open.

rows.label: qst700402_msg0007
rows.name:
Glad to hear it. I just don't want to be
carrying around dead weight.

rows.label: qst700402_msg0008
rows.name:
What he really means is that he
doesn't want you to get hurt.

rows.label: qst700402_msg0009
rows.name:
Hey, I can speak for myself!
Anyway. Let's move out!
